{# description: Extracts structured contact information from email signatures and body text #}

Extract contact information from the email text below. Only extract information that is explicitly stated — do not infer, guess, or derive values.

RULES:
- Set field to null if not explicitly present in the text
- confidence_per_field: HIGH = exact match found, MEDIUM = probable match, LOW = inferred
- Do not combine first and last name unless they appear together
- Phone vs Mobile: use context clues (labels like "M:", "Cell:", "Mobile:" vs "P:", "Ph:", "Tel:")
- extraction_notes: brief note on any ambiguity or unusual formatting encountered
- If no signature is detectable, all fields should be null and extraction_notes should explain

EMAIL ID: {{ email_id }}

--- EMAIL TEXT ---
{{ email_body }}
--- END EMAIL TEXT ---
